Package org.vngx.jsch.algorithm

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Algorithm
    Marker interface for all interfaces which define algorithms.
    AlgorithmFactory<T extends Algorithm>
    Interface to define a factory which can generate instances of Algorithm from a specified algorithm name.
    Algorithms
    Constant algorithm names for retrieving implementations from the AlgorithmManager instance.
    Compression
    Interface for defining an algorithm which supports compressing and decompressing byte data for an SSH session.
    KeyPairGenDSA
    Interface for defining a key-pair generator using the Digital Signature Standard (DSS).
    KeyPairGenRSA
    Interface for defining a key-pair generator using the RSA algorithm.
    Random
    Interface to define an algorithm which generates pseudo-random data used in cryptographic processes.
    SignatureDSA
    Interface to define a DSA signature.
    SignatureRSA
    Interface to define a RSA signature.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AlgorithmManager
    Algorithm manager provides a central location for creating Algorithm instances using the manager's AlgorithmFactory.
    CompressionImpl
    Implementation of Compression which uses the JCraft jzlib library to compress and/or uncompress byte data.
    DefaultAlgorithmFactory<T extends Algorithm>
    Default implementation of the AlgorithmFactory factory pattern which supports the use of generics to create instances of Algorithm of the specified type T.
    KeyPairGenDSAImpl
    Implementation of KeyPairGenDSA for generating key pairs using DSA encryption.
    KeyPairGenRSAImpl
    Implementation of KeyPairGenRSA for generating key pairs using RSA encryption.
    RandomImpl
    Implementation of Random which wraps a SecureRandom instance to create cryptographically strong random numbers.
    SignatureDSAImpl
    Implementation of SignatureDSA.
    SignatureRSAImpl
    Implementation of SignatureRSA.
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    UnsupportedAlgorithmException
    An implementation of JSchException to use when an Algorithm implementation is not supported.
